      <title>美国指控五人犯下“分散式蜘蛛”黑客事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/us-accuses-five-in-scattered-spider-cybercrime-spree</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周三公布的一份诉状和起诉书，美国检察官指控臭名昭著的“散布蜘蛛”团伙的五名成员对数十家公司和个人发动了黑客攻击，导致敏感数据和至少 1100 万美元的加密货币被盗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/us-accuses-five-in-scattered-spider-cybercrime-spree</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 18:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
